name: NOPE
description:
Politics rebellion style. 
A expression of our political views inspired by the design from a famous artist that tells us to Obey, we added our own twist to the game and try to bring light the distressing issue the country faces today. A portion of proceeds will go to support the Obama campain. 

Sizes 
Men: L, XL, XXL
Women: M, L, XL

name: Rebellion Stars The Flagship
description:
One of classic designs from the camp. 
Designed by Rebellion artist Skrybe, it showcases the Rebellion Star logo enveloped with a lovely vine sequence and "rastaesque" colors. 
$250.00 price for this hand crafted custom will be for 
Adidas Stan Smith
Nike AF1
Adidas Superstar
Nike Cortez 
Nike Ace 83
Price is subject to change for desired shoes not listed in this category.

We just use the shoes for a canvas.
